241
00:22:16.827 --> 00:22:18.896
Half hour or so.

242
00:22:20.655 --> 00:22:21.793
I take it

243
00:22:21.896 --> 00:22:23.482
- you called?
- I did.

244
00:22:23.620 --> 00:22:25.206
