who's likely off the wagon.

263
00:23:37.586 --> 00:23:38.655
Likely?

264
00:23:38.758 --> 00:23:40.310
<i>No me jodas. Kino.</i>

265
00:23:40.413 --> 00:23:42.172
[sighs]

266
00:23:43.793 --> 00:23:45.034
<i>Puto Rob-Will.</i>

267
00:23:45.137 --> 00:23:48.482
